index.NAME: Saituna Consulting
index.TITLE_ADVENTAGE4: Direct communication without appointment in the office
index.DESC_ADVENTAGE1: During a 30-minute telephone call, you can discuss your questions about your establishment with your lawyer. For the telephone conversation the lawyer arranges an individual appointment with you.
index.DESC_ADVENTAGE2: Your lawyer will answer questions on all legal issues. For a tax or tax consultancy, which is not included, he recommends a tax consultant on request.
index.DESC_ADVENTAGE3: You can ask individual questions and get binding answers. Your lawyer will advise you on your concerns and give you clear recommendations for your job
index.DESC_ADVENTAGE4: You can communicate with your lawyer via our platform, by e-mail or by telephone. You do not have to make an on-site visit to a law firm.
